  He felt as if there were gaps we had not covered on our travels and he went back throw to check those out.  He journey was detained when two ghouls came to him.  They came with him with stakes and a blade.  They were bound to cut off his head.  They were acting on orders by some one.  He wanted to find out.  The first one came at him with the stake, he diverted the thrust and grabbed his opponents' hand, while in doing so he heard a snap and then saw bone.  The ghoul screamed in pain and fell to his knees. The other ghoul dropped the blade and tried to run, but Willard grabbed him, &quot;Who is you master?&quot;  he said, but the ghoul would not answer.  The next the Willard remembers is the stake plunged into his body for a week he lay in the sewers, no one knew. No one came.  But one day, a member of his clan saw him.  He pulled the stake out and said, &quot;I shouldn't be doing this.  In this place we trust none, but I have pity.  Run, back to where you are safe.  I would run too but I belong here.  I will cover your tracks.  It is not you the he seeks.  It is Sara.&quot;<br>
  Willard then stopped his story to look at me.  &quot;He knew your name.  I could let you go if that is what you wish.  Do you wish to be turned.  He wants to turn you.  You would not be the monster that I am and....&quot;<br>
  &quot;SHHH...&quot; I cued, &quot;I have but one love and that is you.  How would I know if the turning would effect my love for you?   How would I live in the absence of love?  I told you before, I would rather die.  Speak not again of the turning.  My soul can't bare the thought of the loss of love that I bear for you.  I beg you go to Steven, seek his help.  He will help us.  He has a fondness for me as I do him.  I trust him.  Please my love, I could not bear loosing you again.&quot;<br>
  &quot;You don't think I can take care of this?&quot;<br>
  &quot;I do but don't have me grieve for you as well.&quot;<br>
  I turned away and started to cry. &quot;I will not ask him, Sara but trust me, it will be handled.  I will keep you safe.&quot;<br>
  The next afternoon I received a phone call for an anonymous person to meet me next Wednesday, at dusk at one of my law firms outside of Santa Clara.  They wanted to contribute to my non-profit organization, Better Research And No Animal Test Foundation, BRANAT Foundation.  This upset me even more.  I begged again for him to seek the help of Steven.  Every day I did this until he gave in. <br>
