  &quot;Hello this is Crowley here.&quot;  he hears on the other side of the phone.<br>
  &quot;Hello Steven, we have met once.  I am Willard.&quot;<br>
  &quot;Willard, Sara's keeper.  I am glad to hear that you are back in town.  I have been protecting her through your leave of absence.&quot;<br>
  &quot;Yes she told me, which is part of the reason why I am calling you.&quot;<br>
  &quot;Really?&quot;  There was an inquisitiveness in Crowley's voice.<br>
  &quot;Yes, can we meet at Sara's house?&quot;<br>
  &quot;I will be there shortly.&quot;<br>
  Willard hung up the phone and strolled down the sewers a little bit more until he came to another hidden panel which opened into a number punch box.  Willard punched a couple numbers and the wall opened before him.  As he walked threw, the wall closed slowly.  He stood in the cellar of Sara's house.  Sara was on a Victorian styled love seat that was covered in red velvet.  She was sleeping.  Willard smiled and went over and kissed her.  &quot;Steven is coming over.  Shall we go upstairs to greet him?&quot;  And he grabbed her hand and lead her upstairs. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=113.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showNextMessage?topicID=113.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=113.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/prefabs/ez/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.threadControl?topicID=113.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/techops.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=113.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=113.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of rep